极的，能够产生吸引作用的感受，或者他的身世、故事、三观、思想能够打动、吸引你，这些特点不需要全部满足，只需要满足其中一两点就足够，就算有魅力。 就我自己的观剧印象而言，绝大部分华裔、华人男性角色在欧美影视剧中的形象和身份都很套路或者标签化，不是LGBTQ群体，就是矮子、胖子、书呆子或者抓马的传统的异教徒式的角色，你不能否认有些可爱的特质，但是只要是清醒的人都明白其中的边缘性，你要是跟我用智障正确来争论，用什么啊普通人也有大智慧，边缘人也有大作为这种揣着明白装糊涂的观点来杠，我不理你，有魅力这个描述要是看不懂，就想想那个角色你会不会去追他和他喜结连理。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IpKbhtfzn7t86EAMaCDcwMzAyMTk2II7w7okGMAA46QtACXIJNDg2MDkyODI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"86 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-7e5407d3ad8e08a49d61bbced61d35dc_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1743652015.537554","card_id":"Q_1888685528414660511","target":{"id":1888685528414660600,"title":"黄金价格会不会迎来暴跌？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1888685528414660511","type":"question","created":1743077720,"answer_count":157,"follower_count":427,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1346,26559],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"2025年以来，金价的价格一路飙升上涨，再接下来会不会迎来一次大跌？"},"attached_info":"CkoIpKbhtfzn7t86EAMaCTExNDIwMzc2MCDYgpW/BjAAOKsDQApyEzE4ODg2ODU1Mjg0MTQ2NjA1MTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"85 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-30e1274542bb5540f711f7c47edf1995_1440w.webp"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1743652015.537843","card_id":"Q_1888599018352894736","target":{"id":1888599018352894700,"title":"用你现在的英语水平翻译这句话「He is a zero」，该怎么翻译？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1888599018352894736","type":"question","created":1743057094,"answer_count":413,"follower_count":453,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[165,20678],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":